title: Neff North Vs. South: Civil
description: Owners Guido Silvestri and Rob Asselin made their runs in the industry for ten years before opening up Civil. You can bet this shop is doing it right. 2006 marked the grand opening of Civil's first location, and when the skate shops of Providence, Rhode Island went out of business, Civil came through and took over. With a third store opening up within the next few months, it's clear there isn't any stopping the true to the industry leaders of Civil.
